# Local audit / handoff workspaces — produced during development, not part
# of the shipped plugin. Each release leaves bundles under magi-audit-*/
# from local self-review runs; .remember/ is a per-session handoff buffer.
# Future telemetry snapshots that should ship (e.g. for the 2026-05-15
# review routine) must live in a path that does not match these entries
# or be force-added with `git add -f`.
.remember/
magi-audit-2.1.1/
magi-audit-2.1.2/
magi-audit-postfix/
.regression/

# Premortem experiment artifacts live on a local-only feature branch
# (see CLAUDE.md "Post-release hardening / Premortem A/B experiment").
# The directory persists on disk after branch checkout to main until the
# operator deletes both the branch and the directory on 2026-05-29.
experiments/
